Package com.intellij.openapi.vfs

Interface VirtualFileListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CvsEntriesManager, CvsStorageSupportingDeletionComponent, PythonPathCache.MyVirtualFileListener, SvnEntriesFileListener, VFSForAnnotationListener, VirtualFileAdapter, VirtualFileContentsChangedAdapter, VirtualFileFilteringListener, VirtualFileUrlChangeAdapter

    public interface VirtualFileListener
extends java.util.EventListener
    Receives notifications about changes in the virtual file system.
    See Also:
    VirtualFileManager.addVirtualFileListener(VirtualFileListener), VirtualFileListener

        default void propertyChanged(VirtualFilePropertyEvent event)
        Fired when a virtual file is renamed from within the IDE, or its writable status is changed. For files renamed externally, fileCreated(VirtualFileEvent) and fileDeleted(VirtualFileEvent) events will be fired.

        event - the event object containing information about the change.
